d quest doesn't improve the world much at all, or even makes it worse. Toda=
y, we are in a crisis. Silicon Valley's best &#8212; our top operators, exi=
ted founders, and most powerful investors &#8212; are almost all on bad que=
sts.</em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line=
-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Trae Stephens of Anduril and Founders F=
und and Markie Wagner of Delphi Labs argue that there is a moral imperative=
 for Silicon Valley&#8217;s best and brightest to pursue, what they call, &=
